Caroline Elizabeth Wilson, British ambassador to China, delivered a heartfelt speech at the "Friendly Shandong, Remarkable Shandong" 2023 Beijing Presenting Event. She expressed her deep love and fondness for Shandong, praising its traditions and culture. She also anticipates to visit again in the future to experience more of Shandong’s hospitality and its exceptional specialties.
